  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the SEDIC study is to test a home based heart failure patient clinical
      follow-up and therapeutic education using telemedicine. This educational follow-up is based
      on an interactive information system (SCAD) including a touch screen personal computer for
      heart failure patient at home. An interactive algorithm has been developed to allow a self
      management teaching to the patient.Furthermore, a specialized nurse provide a clinical data
      follow-up.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
